{"summary":"<p>linux/unix下的awk、sed是常用的功能强大的文本处理工具，但mac中的这些工具与普通的linux不同。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>例如想以”:”分割$PATH中路径，如果使用普通linux可以使用如下命令</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p><span class=\"pln\">echo $PATH </span><span class=\"pun\">|</span><span class=\"pln\"> sed </span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">e </span><span class=\"str\">‘s/:/\\n/g’</span><br>但如果在mac下就不行了，需要使用以下的几种方式</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://nlfiedler.github.io/2010/12/05/newlines-in-sed-on-mac.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"pln\">echo $PATH</span><span class=\"pun\">|</span><span class=\"pln\">sed </span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">e </span><span class=\"str\">‘s/:/\\’$’</span><span class=\"pln\">\\n</span><span class=\"pun\">/</span><span class=\"pln\">g</span><span class=\"str\">‘<br></span></a>or</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10748453/replace-comma-with-newline-in-sed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"pln\">echo $PATH</span><span class=\"pun\">|</span><span class=\"pln\">sed </span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">e $</span><span class=\"str\">‘s/:/\\\\n/g’<br></span></a>or</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10748453/replace-comma-with-newline-in-sed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"pln\">echo $PATH</span><span class=\"pun\">|</span><span class=\"pln\">sed </span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">e </span><span class=\"str\">‘</span><span class=\"pln\">s</span><span class=\"pun\">/:/</span><span class=\"pln\">\\</span></a></p>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10748453/replace-comma-with-newline-in-sed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"pun\">/</span><span class=\"pln\">g</span><span class=\"str\">‘</span></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>如果想在mac下使用gnu的awk、sed可以安装gawk\\gnu-sed</p>\n<ol>\n<li><span class=\"pln\">brew install gawk</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"pln\">brew install gnu</span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">sed</span></li>\n</ol>\n"}